      "content": "but what if it doesn't get better? everyone says that but it just feels like a lie people tell to keep you moving. the thought of another morning of this... just the silence and the emptiness... it doesn't feel like something i'm supposed to endure. it feels like a punishment. it would be so much easier if i could just... stop. if the noise would just stop for good.",
